entry.title: New York Emerges From the Haze as Canadian Wildfire Smoke Moves South
entry.content: The changing picture will bring relief to millions who have been choked this week by thick smoke and hazy skies. The smoke is expected to move south, but conditions will be much less severe.

entry.title: Donald Trump Indictments Set Historical Marker
entry.content: Other presidents have been impeached or left office in disgrace, but none has ever found himself in the legal jeopardy that now imperils Donald Trump.
